<li id="cite&#95;note-99"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-99">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Thai ethnicity is rather a question of cultural identity than of genetic origin.<sup id="cite&#95;ref-Thak&#95;97-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Thak-97"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>87<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup> Many people in Bangkok who self-identify as Thai have at least some Chinese ancestry.<sup id="cite&#95;ref-98" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-98"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>88<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></span>
